name: Time Isn't Linear
description: Time and energy intertwine. Is time an illusion or ever-expanding in all directions? Is it a reflection of change? An artificial construct of human mentality? Is time something our brains have created - as something that is flowing, ever flowing? Is everything that has ever been and ever will be, happening right now? Are we moving forwards or backwards or in all directions? Whatever time is, itâ€™s best to have a good time.
